    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>The box may best come from <placeName ref="pl0603">Greenock</placeName> to
                        <placeName ref="pl0002">Chester</placeName> by y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> friend who is so kind as to undertake the charge. Let it be left at
                        <persName ref="pe0173">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Monks
                        Bookseller</persName> in that city.</p>
                <p>Pray send me no more <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0064">magazines</title></bibl> by post. for it gives my friend <persName ref="pe0015">Sir Roger</persName> trouble to no purpose. if anything very
                    curious occurs in a single sheet, It may be worth sending.</p>
                <closer><salute>I am Dr Sir <lb/>y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> mos<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName>.</signed>

                <dateline>June 9<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi> 1775.</dateline></closer>


            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
